headline: 2 More Stocks With 1,000% Upside
summary: Tom Yeung here with your Sunday Digest. Almost every multimillionaire investor I know has their version of “The One” – a single investment that built much of their wealth. Several family friends purchased Sun Microsystems in the 1980s after Sun’s cutting-edge workstations left a major impression.
